Company Overview of Spencer Capital Holdings Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Spencer Capital Holdings Ltd. is a holding company, which through its subsidiaries provides reinsurance services to auto dealers. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Hamilton, Bermuda.


50 Cedar AvenueCrawford House1st FloorHamilton,  HM 11BermudaFounded in 2011



Phone: 787-723-8520

www.spencerre.com/parent-company







