Spencer Capital Holdings Ltd. Key Developments

Spencer Capital Holdings Appoints Stephen Roseman as New President
Jun 23 16
Spencer Capital Holdings announced that Stephen Roseman has been appointed as its new president. Ken Shubin Stein will remain CEO and chairman of the company. Roseman will maintain his role as CEO of Spencer Capital Advisors. Roseman has worked in the financial services industry for more than 20 years at firms including Calamos Investments, Kern Capital Management, and Oppenheimer Funds. He also served as CEO and portfolio manager at Thesis Fund Management. Roseman joined as CEO of Spencer Capital Advisors in June of 2015.


